title: Support for Widgets
description: Add support for pre-built and custom widgets/ imbedded content. Will enable users to include useful real-time info, and monitor services directly from Dashy.

title: New & Improved UI Config Editor
description:
The JSON-based config editor can be cumbersome to use, especially for new users. It also does not align with the YAML-based config file. 

This milestone is focused on the development of a much more intuitive UI editor, with features like Drag and Drop, easy edit, etc

This will allow the user to:
- Enter edit mode
	- Only if not disabled + user must be admin
- Modify Sections
	- Add section
	- Delete section
	- Edit section
	- Reorder sections
- Modify Items
	- Add item
	- Delete item
	- Edit item
	- Reorder item
- Modify Page Info
	- Edit title
	- Edit subtitle
	- Edit footer
- Save Changes
	- Write changes to disk
	- Save changes locally
	- Export changes to YAML
	- Cancel, and reset changes
